    "_note": "Canonical JEAB-complete preamble. All four recommended annotator categories are represented: Subjects (@species, @strain, @deprivation, @n), Apparatus (@chamber, @operandum), Procedure (@reinforcer, @clock), Measurement (@session_end, @baseline, @steady_state, @dependent_measure, @logging, @warmup_exclude). Demonstrates orthogonal composition of annotators per architecture.md §4.7.2."
